 * clients can spoof X-Forwarded-For and evade the limiter.
 *
 * @param {Object} [options]
 * @param {number} [options.windowMs=60000]  Window size in milliseconds.
 * @param {number} [options.maxRequests=100] Max requests allowed per window.
 * @param {number} [options.cleanupIntervalMs=60000] How often to sweep idle IPs.
 * @param {(req) => string} [options.keyGenerator] Custom client key extractor.
 * @returns {Function} Express middleware with a `.close()` method.
 */
